\c 53
\s Ubuthutha lobubi babantu
\d Kumqondisi wokuhlabelela. NgeMahalathi. Masikili. EsikaDavida
\p
\v 1 Isithutha sithi enhliziyweni yaso: KakulaNkulunkulu\x + Hlab. 14.1-7.\x*. Bonakele, benza ububi obunengekayo; kakho owenza okuhle\x + Roma 3.10-12.\x*.
\v 2 UNkulunkulu wakhangela phansi esemazulwini phezu kwabantwana babantu, ukubona ukuthi ukhona yini oqedisisayo, odinga uNkulunkulu\x + Roma 3.10-12.\x*.
\v 3 Bonke ngamunye wabo\x + Roma 3.10-12.\x* babuyele emuva, bonke bonakele\x + Hlab. 35.4.\x*; kakho owenza okuhle, kakho loyedwa.
\v 4 Kabazi yini bonke abenzi bobubi, abadla abantu bami \add njengoba\add* besidla isinkwa? Kababizi uNkulunkulu\x + Hlab. 94.4.\x*.
\v 5 Lapho besaba lokwesaba, kungekho okwesabekayo\x + Levi 26.17.\x*. Ngoba uNkulunkulu\x + Hlab. 14.5.\x* uchithachithe\x + Hlab. 89.10. 147.16. Hez. 6.5.\x*\x + Hlab. 141.7.\x* amathambo akhe omisa inkamba emelane lawe\x + Hlab. 141.7.\x*; ubayangisile, ngoba uNkulunkulu ubadelile.
\p
\v 6 Kungathi insindiso zikaIsrayeli zingavela eZiyoni! Lapho uNkulunkulu ebuyisa ukuthunjwa kwabantu bakhe, uJakobe uzathaba, uIsrayeli athokoze.
